1. TestNG is a testing framework for the Java programming language inspired by JUnit and NUnit.
   TestNG provides full control over the test cases and the execution of the test cases. 
   In TestNG, NG stands for "Next Generation".
   TestNG act as a Java Compiler and execute test cases.
   TestNG executes test cases in method.

2. To install TestNG in Eclipse : Help > Eclipse Market Place > Search TestNG and Install

3. XML hierarchy : Test Suit > Test Folder(Module) > Test Cases > Methods